</div>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="footnotes-footer">
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-1"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-1')">1</a>. Given recent events, it is unlikely that this is of any consequence. <a href="/scp-1326">Our usual collection process</a> has been recalled. — H.L.</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-2"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-2')">2</a>. Unlike the Foundation, we do not possess troops and automated weaponries. For all their faults, they were dreadfully efficacious. — H.L.</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-3"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-3')">3</a>. Perhaps, they were all swept up in a conspiracy and left me willfully in silence. I would not know. — H.L.</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-4"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-4')">4</a>. It is a sad thing for a library to wither. — H.L.</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-5"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-5')">5</a>. I will not carry over the traditional title of &quot;Jailer&quot;. It is a cruel thing, to be given a name you do not want. — H.L.</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-6"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-6')">6</a>. Manipulation of the <a href="/scp-3662">Noosphere</a> to expunge knowledge of this operation is suspected; they would have had the technology at the time. — H.L.</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-7"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-7')">7</a>. I cannot forgive you as my master might have, but I pray I may understand. — H.L.</div>
</div>
